messages.content: I love going to art galleries and museums on weekends. The SFMOMA is one of my favorite places.
Just got back from an amazing jazz concert at the Blue Note. Live music really energizes me.
Thinking about taking a cooking workshop this weekend. I've been really into learning new cuisines lately.
The tech conference last week was incredible. I especially loved the AI and machine learning sessions.
Went hiking in Marin County yesterday. Nature photography workshop sounds interesting too.
Book reading at City Lights was so inspiring. I should go to more literary events.
The food festival in Golden Gate Park was amazing. Street food and live music - perfect combination!
Thinking about joining a yoga class. Mind-body wellness events seem really appealing lately.
